cmines - A public domain mine-seeking game.
===

This project was made with the aim to provide
a high-quality and fun to play minesweeper game,
without any licensing restrictions.

It can be built using the provided makefile, and
the `all` target.

To install, run `sudo make install`, and to
uninstall, `sudo make uninstall`

Please see `LICENSE` for a clear description for the
project license.

Contributions are more than welcome. As of right now
there's no contributor guidelines, so just try to
follow the overall style of the project, and we should
be fine.